 What is a Job ?
 &lt;a href="#what-is-a-job-" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink to this heading">ðŸ”—&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>A Job is used to launch batch-jobs. It can either:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>launch a single Pod&lt;/li>
&lt;li>launch several Pods in parallel or in sequence&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>

